title: >-
  Governing Agentic Software Development with Executable Evidence:
  Mechanical Gates, Human Review, and Skill Capitalization
type: report
authors:
  - family-names: Lu
    given-names: Yeh-Hsing
    affiliation: "Tiger AI Tech Co., Ltd., Taiwan"
